item.title: About Me
item.description: My name is Yii Kuo Chong, people call me Brandon. I write code for a living. Sometimes at full time positions, sometimes I take on projects. A fortune teller in Taipei once told me that it’s important to take the first steps than to be afraid of failure. That’s what I’m doing. This website is a personal blog which I use to document my learning journey and share my work with the world.
